---
---

<section id="why" class="why-section">
  <div class="divider"></div>
  <div style="height:7rem;"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label"><span>Why Rotacut</span></div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Engineering That Sets Us Apart</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">
      Every Rotacut cutter is built on six engineering principles that ensure maximum performance on
      every cut.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="usp-grid">
    <div class="usp-item">
      <div class="usp-number">01</div>
      <div class="usp-title">Sandvik Carbide Tips</div>
      <p class="usp-text">
        Extremely hard and durable tungsten carbide cutting teeth sourced from Sandvik — the world's
        leading carbide manufacturer — for the hardest drilling tasks.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="usp-item">
      <div class="usp-number">02</div>
      <div class="usp-title">Optimised Cutting Geometry</div>
      <p class="usp-text">
        Offset tooth positioning and continuous pre-cut design delivers the lowest heat development
        and burr-free finishes on every hole.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="usp-item">
      <div class="usp-number">03</div>
      <div class="usp-title">Precision Ground Shanks</div>
      <p class="usp-text">
        Weldon 19.05mm and Universal 31.75mm shank options with close-tolerance fitment for zero
        run-out and maximum concentricity.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="usp-item">
      <div class="usp-number">04</div>
      <div class="usp-title">Optimal Chip Removal</div>
      <p class="usp-text">
        Engineered spiral flute angles designed for maximum chip evacuation efficiency — keeping the
        cut clean, cool, and consistent.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="usp-item">
      <div class="usp-number">05</div>
      <div class="usp-title">Stability &amp; Durability</div>
      <p class="usp-text">
        Special alloy body with tapered inside fitment prevents the cutter from getting stuck —
        protecting both the cutter and your magnetic drill.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="usp-item">
      <div class="usp-number">06</div>
      <div class="usp-title">Complete Size Range</div>
      <p class="usp-text">
        Diameters from 11mm to 65mm, cutting depths from 25mm to 100mm. Custom sizes available on
        request for OEM and special applications.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why-section {
    background: var(--bg2);
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .usp-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .usp-item {
    background: var(--bg2);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .usp-item::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 3px;
    height: 0;
    background: var(--red);
    transition: height 0.4s ease;
  }

  .usp-item:hover::after {
    height: 100%;
  }

  .usp-number {
    font-family: "Bebas Neue", sans-serif;
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: rgba(204, 0, 0, 0.1);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .usp-title {
    font-family: "Bebas Neue", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .usp-text {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .usp-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
